dct_title_s: Automobile routes from Los Angeles to Bakersfield via coast route
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; H.P.H.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Includes legend and table of distances.
Numbered 64 in lower left corner and 25 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
